STATE of North Carolina
v.
Daniel LUNA No. 406P17-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 25, 2018 Daniel Luna, for Luna, Daniel. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Ben R. David, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 24th of May 2018 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, New Hanover County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 25th of May 2018."
